ZH: 他们希望通过仲裁解决他们之间的争端。
EN: They hope to resolve their disputes through arbitration.

ZH: 仲裁机构的决定对各方都有约束力。
EN: The decisions of arbitration bodies are binding on all parties involved.

ZH: 这次仲裁是非常公正和公平的。
EN: This arbitration is extremely fair and just.

ZH: 仲裁程序通常要比法庭诉讼快速和高效。
EN: Arbitration proceedings are usually quicker and more efficient than courtroom litigation.

ZH: 在双方无法达成协议的情况下，仲裁是一个可行的选择。
EN: Arbitration is a viable option when the parties cannot reach an agreement.

ZH: 我们将提请仲裁来解决这起合同纠纷。
EN: We will seek arbitration to resolve this contract dispute.

ZH: 仲裁解决争端可以避免长期的法律程序。
EN: Arbitration for dispute resolution can avoid lengthy legal proceedings.

ZH: 我们必须按照仲裁裁决来执行。
EN: We must comply with the arbitration award.

ZH: 仲裁员的任务是公正地评估双方的证据。
EN: The arbitrator's task is to impartially evaluate the evidence presented by both parties.

ZH: 仲裁员必须保持中立和独立。
EN: Arbitrators must maintain neutrality and independence.

ZH: 他们同意将争议提交仲裁。
EN: They agreed to submit the dispute to arbitration.

ZH: 仲裁方案已经公开透明地公布给相关方。
EN: The arbitration scheme has been publicly disclosed to the relevant parties.

ZH: 仲裁机构有权力裁决争议的结果。
EN: The arbitration body has the authority to decide the outcome of the dispute.

ZH: 仲裁是一种私下解决争议的方式。
EN: Arbitration is a way to resolve disputes privately.

ZH: 仲裁要求双方遵守仲裁条款和程序。
EN: Arbitration requires both parties to adhere to the arbitration clauses and procedures.

ZH: 仲裁协议一旦达成，双方必须遵守其约定。
EN: Once an arbitration agreement is reached, both parties must abide by its terms.

ZH: 他们正在寻求仲裁员的帮助来解决纠纷。
EN: They are seeking the assistance of an arbitrator to resolve their dispute.

ZH: 仲裁文书是该案件的正式记录。
EN: The arbitration award is the official record of the case.

ZH: 仲裁过程的机密性保护了各方的商业利益。
EN: The confidentiality of the arbitration process protects the commercial interests of all parties.

